    "Blockchain creates a record of data transactions and modifications that are viewable by all nodes in the blockchain.",
    "This transparency helps establish trust among different business domains and enables participants to verify the integrity and the history of the shared datasets.",
    "• Federated Governance and Control: Since our framework uses blockchain, it allows for establishing rules and policies governing datasets structure, access, and usage.",
    "By leveraging smart contracts transactions in the blockchain, our framework can enforce data governance processes, ensuring that datasets that are shared follow the predefined rules and guidelines that are agreed upon by the participating domains.",
    "• Data Security and Privacy: Blockchain's cryptographic protocols can enhance data security and privacy within a data mesh."
